data.description:
Better than new! Welcome home to this impeccably maintained home in the centrally located community of Hearthstone Lakes. Designed for seamless entertaining and comfortable living, the open-concept layout connects the formal dining room, living room, and cozy family room around a chef-inspired kitchen. The gourmet kitchen is exceptional, featuring a wrap-around breakfast bar, a built-in oven, top-tier stainless steel appliances, and sleek granite countertops. All of this happens under impressive 10 ft. ceilings, complemented by elegant crown molding and transom windows.The home's thoughtful split-bedroom design maximizes both privacy and functionality. On one side, discover two bedrooms and a generously sized laundry room. Retreat to the master suite on the opposite end, where you'll find a multi-purpose sitting area and a spa-like ensuite bath complete with a grand shower, a private water-closet, double-vanity, a beautiful walk-in-closet. Venture outdoors to find a covered patio that's perfect for any get-together. 
As a former model home, every inch of this residence has been meticulously upgraded and maintained. Schedule your private showing! Back on market at not fault of the seller - you have a second chance at this beautiful home
